OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,FA non-profit company from Bolton has
OL,7,Fhanded in a petition to 10 Downing
OL,8,FStreet calling for #100m from fines
OL,9,Flevied by the Financial Conduct
OL,10,FAuthority (FCA) to be redirected to
OL,11,Ffund hospices.
OL,13,FThe Box Power CIC campaign, run by a
OL,14,Fnot-for-profit energy consultancy, was
OL,15,Foriginally sparked by a Change.org
OL,16,Fpetition; now over 60 Members of
OL,17,FParliament and peers, alongside 30
OL,18,Fhospices, have come together to
OL,19,Fsupport the campaign.
