OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,FWhen Box Power CIC first launched the
OL,7,Fcampaign, hospices across the UK were
OL,8,Falready facing a #70 million funding
OL,9,Fshortfall.
OL,11,FSince then, job losses and reduced
OL,12,Fhours have been announced at several
OL,13,Fhospices, worsening the situation.
OL,15,FNHS contributions cover just 10% to
OL,16,F25% of hospices' operating costs, and
OL,17,Forganisations like Hospice UK are
OL,18,Fcalling on the government for a long-
OL,19,Fterm, sustainable funding solution.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
