OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,FCorin Dalby said: "It's heartbreaking
OL,7,Fto see hospices, which have tirelessly
OL,8,Fraised funds to stay open, struggle to
OL,9,Fcover even the most basic operating
OL,10,Fcosts.
OL,12,F"Some hospices have raised money to
OL,13,Fbuild rooms that are left empty
OL,14,Fbecause they simply can't afford to
OL,15,Fstaff them, placing added pressure on
OL,16,Falready stretched donations.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
