OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,F"Despite the fact that a well-funded
OL,7,Fhospice sector would ease the burden
OL,8,Fon the NHS and social care, hospices
OL,9,Freceive only 20-33% of their funding
OL,10,Ffrom the state."
OL,12,FDalby continued: "The FCA fines, which
OL,13,Ftotal hundreds of millions each year,
OL,14,Fare generally levied as a result of
OL,15,Ffinancial injustices that impact the
OL,16,FUK public.
OL,26,@rD@PO]tD@ROU
