OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,F"There is no better way to address
OL,7,Fthese injustices than by directing
OL,8,Fthese funds to the hospice sector,
OL,9,Fwhich directly improves the lives of
OL,10,Fthe most vulnerable in society."
OL,12,FThe campaign comes at a time when
OL,13,Fsignificant FCA fines have been handed
OL,14,Fdown to financial institutions.
OL,16,FJust last week, Barclays was fined #40
OL,17,Fmillion and Macquarie Bank #13
OL,18,Fmillion, bringing the total FCA fines
OL,19,Ffor the year to #174 million.
