OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,FOne of the Hospices that have shown
OL,7,Ftheir support is Bury Hospice and at
OL,8,Fthe last budget meeting, it was clear
OL,9,Fthey had a deficit.
OL,11,FJulie Thew's son Christian received
OL,12,Fsupport from Bury Hospice after he was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with advanced pancreatic
OL,14,Fcancer and was given months to live.
OL,16,FShe's raised more than 50 thousand
OL,17,Fpounds for the hospice but says
OL,18,Fkeeping the doors open at an essential
OL,19,Fpublic service should not fall to
OL,20,Ffundraisers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
