OL,3,CMPs back campaign for FCA fines to go
OL,4,Ctoward supporting Hospices
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said that
OL,7,Fmoney from FCA fines already go
OL,8,Fstraight into funding public services,
OL,9,Fincluding the NHS.
OL,11,FThey added: "We are determined to
OL,12,Fshift more healthcare into the
OL,13,Fcommunity and ensure patients and
OL,14,Ftheir families receive high-quality,
OL,15,Fpersonalised care in the most
OL,16,Fappropriate setting, and hospices will
OL,17,Fhave a big role to play in that shift.
OL,18,F"
